<div class="container">
  <header class="post-header">
    <h1 class="post-title">Ranking da categoria Sênior</h1>
  </header>

  <div class="post-content">
    <p>A categoria sênior reúne os competidores mais experientes da região.</p>

    <div class="table-responsive">

    <table class="table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Nome</th>
          <th>Handle do Codeforces</th>
          <th style="text-align: right">Rating do Codeforces</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>

        <% User.senior.each do |user| %>
          <tr>
            <td> <%= user.name %> </td>
            <td> <%= link_to user.handle, "https://codeforces.com/profile/#{user.handle}" %> </td>
            <td style="text-align: right">  <%= user.rating %> </td>
          </tr>
        <%end %>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  </div>
